nt - you can deliver parcels or cargo, mine and sell resources, or you can open your own store and sell goods to the inhabitants of the island.</li></ul><br>Explore a large island that has become your new home. Get resources on the island and use them to build your house. Earn money and expand your estate, buy new furniture and renovate your house - everything is available from painting the walls and wallpapering to installing your own elevator. Buy new cars for the convenience of moving around the island and earning money.",
